1
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:34,960
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,289 --> 00:01:37,789
[Episode 14]

3
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:16,520
Ren Susu?

4
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:18,310
Why is it her?

5
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:21,710
