So full of himself.

8
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,240
So it's Mr. No. 9.

9
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,870
You truly have a good eye.

10
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:37,590
So he's the legendary No. 9.

11
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,750
Why's he so unreasonable?

12
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,120
He just outright asked for her.

13
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,310
Why the rush, sir?

14
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,360
In front of everyone,

15
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,290
