Restore it.

22
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,840
No. 9 sure lives up to his name.

23
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,030
Very experienced.

24
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,470
First time seeing

25
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:42,270
