26
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:55,680
Get her out.

27
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,080
Why are you here?

28
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,840
If you can act independently

29
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,600
and come here to save others,

30
00:04:16,190 --> 00:04:17,120
can't I come

31
