She was supposed to be on stage now.

34
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:30,960
I'm standing in for her.

35
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,920
You're mine now.

36
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:36,430
I'll take you out.

37
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,630
No.

38
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:44,360
Ye Zhihong and the other girls
are trapped inside.

39
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,820
I can't just abandon them.

40
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:48,070
I need to stall for time,

41
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:49,920
so Yinwei and the rest

42
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,520
have a chance to rescue them.

43
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,360
What's your plan?

44
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:55,800
Muddy the waters, of course.

45
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,159
It's easier to make a move amid chaos.

46
00:04:57,210 --> 00:05:01,810
♪ Forgive me, I've loved you for ages ♪

47
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,930
♪ Please lull me into absolute surrender ♪

48
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:08,860
♪ Before you cage me
in a prison of your design ♪

49
00:05:09,690 --> 00:05:14,160
♪ Stop bowing to the crowd ♪

50
