we don't have to go to the vault?

54
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,000
You're needed more here.

55
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:32,070
If we assassinate that darn old Huo here,

56
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,630
we can draw away the Huos' main forces.

57
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,310
Then Susu will have a better chance

58
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:36,510
to save those inside.

59
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:38,750
Do you think

60
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:41,040
Susu will be in danger?

61
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,040
In our journey,

62
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:45,120
which step hasn't been dangerous?

63
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,310
To save others,

64
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,860
