65
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,240
Look at these animals.

66
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,190
What now?

67
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,510
The show's over.

68
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,620
We can't stall any longer.

69
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,910
Who says the show's over?

70
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:09,000
I can buy more time

71
