72
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,850
It's all in my plans.

73
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:18,920
Do it.

74
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,950
Hurry up, No. 9!

75
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,280
You can't do it, can you?

76
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,270
You wimp!

77
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,310
Replace him!

78
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,870
-Replace him!
-Replace him!

79
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,270
Ren Susu,

80
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,080
you're really going all out.

81
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:53,920
♪ Fantasies reduced to ash ♪

82
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:56,100
♪ In a raging fire ♪

83
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:58,510
When you grow up in hell,
you naturally

84
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,360
understand that

85
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,810
♪ Those caught in the wake ♪

86
00:07:01,190 --> 00:07:02,430
only by being ruthless

87
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,950
♪ Now tell only gray lies ♪

88
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:03,830
and decisive

89
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,360
can you drag the evil

90
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,950
into the darkness with you.

91
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:09,050
♪ Willingly ♪

92
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:11,060
♪ Surrendering the naive visage ♪

93
00:07:12,100 --> 00:07:14,240
♪ Of the past ♪

94
00:07:18,130 --> 00:07:20,330
♪ With no expectation of dawn ♪

95
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,920
You're as ruthless to others as ever,

96
00:07:24,140 --> 00:07:27,010
♪ Wandering beneath a pitch-black sky ♪

97
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:29,410
♪ I smell no sorrow ♪

98
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,160
and even more so to yourself.

99
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:32,800
Forgotten the lesson
of the bloody wedding dress already?

100
00:07:32,010 --> 00:07:34,470
♪ Let the story start over ♪

101
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,000
You really never learn.

102
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:37,230
♪ With a new beginning ♪

103
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:40,480
Innocent people?

104
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:41,740
♪ Willingly ♪

105
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,390
She's innocent?

106
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,890
♪ Surrendering the naive visage ♪

107
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,000
You're always like this,

108
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:46,990
♪ Of the past ♪

109
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:48,620
