110
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,210
That's why you get fooled.

111
00:07:50,690 --> 00:07:53,190
♪ With no expectation of dawn ♪

112
00:08:01,070 --> 00:08:03,800
Then I have to be more ruthless
than you just once,

113
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,680
to beat you once.

114
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,000
She can only be mine!

115
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:17,440
♪ Forgive me, I've loved you for ages ♪

116
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:21,450
♪ Please lull me into absolute surrender ♪

117
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:24,450
♪ Before you cage me
in a prison of your design ♪

118
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:29,620
♪ Just you and me, all else fades away ♪

119
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,070
Inspector Li,

120
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,240
it's so late.

121
00:08:37,549 --> 00:08:38,480
I can just

122
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,809
patrol with the others.

123
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,409
Go back and rest early.

124
00:08:41,789 --> 00:08:42,480
It's fine.

125
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:45,080
Hasn't there been a crime wave lately?

126
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,280
It's good to have an extra pair of hands.

127
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,670
But as for you,

128
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,030
hasn't your mother

129
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:51,290
fallen sick recently?

130
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:52,550
These few days,

131
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:53,350
go home early.

132
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,970
Is this batch of goods from the vault
all sent out?

133
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,140
Yes, Grandfather.

134
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,640
They're all sent out.

135
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,790
That girl I sent over

136
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,500
must not be left alive.

137
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,800
Rest assured.

138
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:20,550
I'll make sure she

139
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,520
wishes she were dead,

140
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,630
before I kill her.

141
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,960
[Hong Fang Bank]

142
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:37,650
Here they come.

143
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,050
What's going on?

144
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,570
Grandfather, get down!

145
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,840
Don't let them get away!

146
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,010
Let's go.

147
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,270
We can't kill him now.

148
00:10:27,270 --> 00:10:29,330
That'd be letting him off too easily.

149
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:37,120
Go!

150
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,510
After them!

151
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:44,360
Let's split up!

152
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:44,870
Yes!

153
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,440
I saw the inspector Li Boze

154
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,440
coming for us too.

155
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,150
You go that way.

156
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,030
I'll deal with Li Boze.

157
00:10:52,030 --> 00:10:53,360
I'll draw away the Huos.

158
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,250
This way!

159
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:01,770
This way!

160
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,000
Stop running.

161
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:31,390
You again?

162
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,990
I should ask you that.

163
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,600
What happened over there?

164
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,200
Shouldn't you go take a look?

165
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:38,000
The loud noise scared me.

166
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,200
I had to run for my life

167
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,490
and even sprained my ankle.

168
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:43,080
Carry me.

169
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:48,760
Why should I?

170
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,240
Why should you?

171
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:52,440
Tell me:

172
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,720
what are the duties of the police?

173
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,840
Enforce the law justly

174
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,550
and protect the people.

175
00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:56,600
Am I not part of the people?

176
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,260
Are you not part of the police?

177
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,750
I was just passing by after rehearsal,

178
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:08,360
when I heard a loud bang.

179
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:09,480
I thought

180
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,030
a sprained ankle was bad enough,

181
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:13,290
but then I bumped into you, Inspector Li.

182
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,230
Boss Hai,

183
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,080
what are the odds?

184
00:12:19,550 --> 00:12:21,010
Wherever there's unrest,

185
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,150
there you are.

186
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:25,250
How about this?

187
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,750
Go back to the station with me

188
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,640
and make a statement.

189
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,270
What are you talking about?

190
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:34,240
I don't understand.

191
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:37,040
Anyway, like the moon
revolving around the earth,

192
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:39,270
you're always revolving around me.

193
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,800
Are you the moon incarnate?

194
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:10,930
Boss Hai...

195
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:15,590
don't you love playing pretend?

196
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:17,630
So why

197
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,910
is your mask

198
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,790
starting to slip?

199
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:28,000
Looking so fierce,

200
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:31,120
this is the real you, huh?

201
00:13:33,390 --> 00:13:34,320
What do you want?

202
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:41,800
I can't do anything.

203
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:44,430
I don't have evidence right now.

204
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,760
But I'll keep my eye on you

205
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,820
until I uncover the truth.

206
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,750
Do you detest me this much?

207
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,450
Then why'd you blush
every time you saw me?

208
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:03,600
Boss Hai,

209
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,480
I won't beat around the bush.

210
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,940
I'll be straight with you.

211
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,320
Although we

212
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,250
haven't known each other for long,

213
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,460
I admit that since I first saw you,

214
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:17,810
I became unspeakably curious about you.

215
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:20,200
It's a curiosity that's

216
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,360
indescribable.

217
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:22,390
I want to know

218
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,510
who you really are.

219
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,120
But I also know
you're hiding a lot of secrets.

220
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:27,750
So...

221
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,030
So you want me to

222
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:33,120
throw myself at you
because of your vague feelings,

223
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,000
before you'll let me go?

224
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,400
I have no such intention.

225
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,240
I just...

226
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,840
I just hope you can

227
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:48,580
voluntarily come back
to the station with me

228
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:49,920
to make a statement.

229
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:53,350
Inspector Li,

230
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:57,120
you and I are from different worlds.

231
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,890
Don't waste your time on me.

232
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:48,850
[Hong Fang Bank]

233
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:52,000
Is anyone there? Help!

234
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,670
She's not breathing! Somebody help!

235
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,080
Is anyone there?

236
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:58,030
Somebody help!

237
00:15:58,030 --> 00:15:59,360
She's not breathing!

238
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,480
Somebody help!

239
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:01,780
Where's everyone?

240
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:04,480
Help! Somebody!

241
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:07,030
-What's wrong? Stop yelling!
-Help!

242
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,720
Please save her!

243
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:10,120
She's not breathing!

244
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,120
She's dead?

245
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:19,500
Is she dead?

246
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:20,360
Drag her out.

247
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:24,080
Shouldn't she be on stage right now?

248
00:16:59,180 --> 00:17:01,930
Help! Open the door!

249
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:10,829
Thanks to the plan you and Miss Fang made,

250
00:17:10,829 --> 00:17:11,640
we're free.

251
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,099
How are you?

252
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:18,000
Are you okay?

253
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:18,920
I'm fine.

254
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:23,000
Can they go out

255
00:17:23,589 --> 00:17:24,550
the way you came in?

256
00:17:24,550 --> 00:17:25,069
Yes.

257
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,450
Don't worry.

258
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:28,210
I'm here to take everyone out.

259
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:29,510
What about Miss Fang?

260
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:30,270
Where is she?

261
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:31,750
Once you reach safety,

262
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:33,210
she'll find a way to leave.

263
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,510
You take them out first.

264
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:35,570
I'll go back her up.

265
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:38,030
Let's not go out with a whimper.

266
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:38,960
We want revenge.

267
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:40,220
We want to save others!

268
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,160
Yes!

269
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,240
We'd rather die

270
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,770
than let those bastards go!

271
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:46,120
Sisters, let's fight them to the death!

272
00:17:58,720 --> 00:17:59,310
Okay.

273
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,830
Let's fight our way out together!

274
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:02,790
Okay!

275
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:09,040
Ms. Wang,

276
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,000
