279
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:19,850
What's this about?

280
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:22,240
You're not No. 9.

281
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:24,000
Not No. 9?

282
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:25,640
Then who is he?

283
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:27,920
You're quite the actor!

284
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:30,110
Who on earth are you?

285
00:18:36,510 --> 00:18:37,910
Who I am isn't important.

286
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:42,750
But if you dare to
mess with me and her today,

287
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:47,240
neither you nor the Huos
will end well.

288
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:50,650
The vault matter must not be exposed!

289
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:51,720
